{{Top|leg}}
'''MSF-F2''' was the original prototype of the [[MSF mouse droid|MSF-series]] [[MSE-6 series repair droid/Legends|mouse droids]]. [[QS-2D]] decided to keep it around [[Uffel]], while the rest of line was sold. It was usually assigned to follow around any visitors to the [[Moon/Legends|moon]]. MSF-F2 was very obvious when it did this, so visitors knew they were being monitored. Most did not mind, but a few did try to give the MSF-F2 the slip. It would always show up again, almost as if it were everywhere at once.

MSF-F2 was a silver-trimmed mouse droid. When it moved along the ground, it would seem to waddle, due to a uneven calibration of its wheel wells.

